Package il.org.spartan

Enum CSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CSV>
      • il.org.spartan.CSV
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CSV>
    public enum CSV
extends java.lang.Enum<CSV>
    This class realize the CSV specification, by comprising methods for manipulating CSV files. e.g. 1, 2, 3 4, 5, 6 The class supports string arrays as data. e.g. 1, "{9; 10}", 3 4, "{8; 11}", 6 This class also supports converting strings to enums instances. e.g. 1, EXTENDS, 3 4, IMPLEMENTS, 6 This is a simplified version of the CSV specification, each record must be a single line. Within are some other useful auxiliary functions for string manipulations.
    Author:
    Oren Rubin
